messages.messageBody:
"You don't have to live there to get it just visit there web site and
send
them an email or call. We've been members for 3 years and have never
even
been there."

There's a center in Fort Walton Beach Florida that is only $45 per
year for a family. You can call them, order your membership on the
phone and get access to hundreds of science museums (like OMSI)
nationwide all year. It's the Emerald Coast Science Center if anyone
wants one.:) They'll tell you who they're affiliated with so check
before you buy.

Ren
